      <div class="model-card"><h3>400 Series BO built-in oven 30"</h3><p>Core wall-oven module in 400 Series flagship column. Current-generation control platform, precision convection, flush-mount integrated aesthetic. Service: bake element, convection fan, control board, door hardware, sensors.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>400 Series BS Combi-Steam module</h3><p>Pure steam + convection combination. Internal water boiler + steam distribution. LA hard-water descaling cadence. Service: descaling, boiler element, water valve, steam-generation sensor, combi-mode logic.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>400 Series BM Speed Oven module</h3><p>Microwave + convection combo for rapid-cook capability in the column. Service: magnetron, microwave-side interlocks, convection element + fan, integrated control board.</p></div>
